<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>bạjy qdạmk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- bạjy qdạmk wạ̉nạ mkswr mḥtạj lmʿwntk sydy
 wạtẖq hạkẖrj byk mnṣwr mrfwʿẗ rạsy wạ̹ydy
 ạlqrạr- mạ ạ̉ʿẓm ḥbk ly wʿml rwḥk yạ fạdy
 lwlạ mrạḥmk rby ʿlynạ lạ mjynạ wlạ njynạ
 2- bạjy qdạmk ʿsẖmạn fyk fy mrạḥmk wḥbk ly
 hạkẖṭy ḥdwdy mạsk bạ̹ydyk bqḍyb nʿmẗ mdwd ly
 3- bạjy qdạmk msẖtạq lyk ʿyny ʿly̱ ạlnʿmẗ wlmsthạ
 zy mạ ʿndy ạ̉nạ ʿyny ʿlyk mntẓr ạlmsḥẗ wqwthạ
 4- bạjy qdạmk bạʿln jwʿy lsẖryʿtk wʿmlk fy
 ạ̹nt ṭlbty yạ yswʿy sẖhwẗ qlby ạlḥqyqyẗ</lyrics>
